  Just a thought.
   
  Misty

bruce halliday <paranormalinvestigating@...> wrote:
          Ann,
 
From what I can discern from mike and Lisa's communication regarding techs/guardians
is that a tech is assigned to a researcher here on earth based on their compatible energy and harmonic vibration.
That is not so easy to do, so every time you do a session there is a temp assigned for that particular session.
 
Give it some more time and keep asking but I'm sure when you do get yours it will be a special relationship.
 
In other words you have to kiss the exact right frog for him to turn into your prince aah or princess 
 
I will keep the subject open with mike and Lisa until I get a definitive answer or you do.
 
Bruce


  Bruce Halliday
